lead_paragraph: Rich Berberian Jr. rallied to win the PGA Professional Championship on Wednesday, holing a 30-foot birdie putt on the final hole for a one-stroke victory.

headline.print_headline: Rich Berberian Jr. Wins PGA Professional Championship
